snippet.title: Endorfun
snippet.description: Endorfun is a colorful puzzle game developed by Onesong and published by Time Warner Interactive in 1995. You control a small cube along a grid and your goal is to collect the textured tiles by rolling over them with the matching color. This game is known for its use of subliminal messages in its soundtracks.
